<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='408800' id='t-408800'>Young students are always asking me</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='410627' id='t-410627'>what these animals are saying,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='412080' id='t-412080'>and really I've got no idea.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='416911' id='t-416911'>But I can tell you that they do
