<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='425258' id='t-425258'>I was walking along the shore in Alaska,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='427586' id='t-427586'>and I came across this tide pool</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='429930' id='t-429930'>filled with a colony of sea anemones,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='432962' id='t-432962'>these wonderful eating machines,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='435038' id='t-435038'>relatives of coral and jellyfish.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='437889' id='t-437889'>And curious to see
