<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='444410' id='t-444410'>down the mouth part,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445598' id='t-445598'>and immediately the critter began</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='447359' id='t-447359'>to absorb the microphone into its belly,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='449568' id='t-449568'>and the tentacles were
searching out of the surface</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='452262' id='t-452262'>for something of nutritional value.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='454673' id='t-454673'>The static-like sounds that are very low,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='457178' id='t-457178'>that you're going to hear right now.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='459182' id='t-459182'>(Static sounds)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='463584' id='t-463584'>Yeah, but watch. When it
didn't find anything to eat --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='466451' id='t-466451'>(Honking sound)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467840' id='t-467840'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='470500' id='t-470500'>I think that's an expression
that can be understood</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='472997' id='t-472997'>in any language.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='474414' id='t-474414'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='479280' id='t-479280'>At the end of its breeding cycle,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='480880' id='t-480880'>the Great Basin Spadefoot toad</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='483036' id='t-483036'>digs itself down about a meter under</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='485111' id='t-485111'>the hard-panned desert
soil of the American West,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='488261' id='t-488261'>where it can stay for many seasons</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='490140' id='t-490140'>until conditions are just
