<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='531886' id='t-531886'>when it's in a very healthy pattern.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='534147' id='t-534147'>(Frogs croaking)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='544163' id='t-544163'>Mono Lake is just to the east
