<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592087' id='t-592087'>four and a half,
and six and a half seconds,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='594279' id='t-594279'>and then the sound
of the jet, the signature,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='597378' id='t-597378'>is in yellow at the very
