<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='599937' id='t-599937'>(Frogs croaking)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='609582' id='t-609582'>Now at the end of that flyby,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='611976' id='t-611976'>it took the frogs fully 45 minutes</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='615465' id='t-615465'>to regain their chorusing synchronicity,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='617869' id='t-617869'>during which time, and under a full moon,</span>
