<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='643144' id='t-643144'>It's a very sad story,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='644618' id='t-644618'>but it really illustrates how animals</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='648496' id='t-648496'>can sometimes show emotion,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='650478' id='t-650478'>a very controversial subject
