<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='716332' id='t-716332'>This is probably the saddest sound</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='719241' id='t-719241'>I've ever heard coming from any organism,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722159' id='t-722159'>human or other.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='726517' id='t-726517'>(Beaver crying)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='742180' id='t-742180'>Yeah. Well.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='743995' id='t-743995'>There are many facets to soundscapes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='746577' id='t-746577'>among them the ways in which animals
